channel.title: More newbie Sigs [Better I think]
channel.description:
I think I've gotten better at this. Though, I still need some more brushes, effects, and all that. Still working on them atm.
[URL=http://img504.imageshack.us/my.php?image=ikesigb.png][IMG]http://img504.imageshack.us/img504/9996/ikesigb.png[/img][/URL] My favorite character in Fire emblem and in SSB Brawl :D
[URL=http://img504.imageshack.us/my.php?image=jinreedited.png][IMG]http://img504.imageshack.us/img504/296/jinreedited.png[/img][/URL] Re-edited my Jin signature, looks better imo.
[URL=http://img504.imageshack.us/my.php?image=link.png][IMG]http://img504.imageshack.us/img504/7444/link.png[/img][/URL] Link and his triforce symbol and name. Gonna make 2 more later, which includes Zelda (Wisdom) and Ganondorf (Power)
[URL=http://img504.imageshack.us/my.php?image=scorpion.png][IMG]http://img504.imageshack.us/img504/5528/scorpion.png[/img][/URL] Scorpion tribute, one of my favorite mortal kombat character.
[URL=http://img504.imageshack.us/my.php?image=subzero.png][IMG]http://img504.imageshack.us/img504/5590/subzero.png[/img][/URL] last but not least, sub-zero. My other favorite mortal kombat character.
This is gonna be my last post in a while. It feels like this is spam :O
